                  THRU S3140-THKJL0018-INSERT-EXT

      *    한도신청번호가 있으면 : 업데이트 건
           ELSE

               MOVE CO-CHA-2          TO WK-BIT

               MOVE XDJL0B18-I-LIMT-APLCN-NO
                 TO WK-LIMT-APLCN-NO

               PERFORM S3120-THKJL0018-SELECT-RTN
                  THRU S3120-THKJL0018-SELECT-EXT

           END-IF

